description:
This is a 26 minute workout called '25 Min CALISTHENICS WORKOUT for Beginners & Intermediates | Follow Along' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Build strength with this 25 minute Calisthenics workout suitable for beginners to intermediates. This bodyweight workout can be done with, or without parallettes. Get GRAVITY FITNESS Parallettes https://gravity.fitness/TOMPETOTRAINING

This routine includes the best bodyweight and beginner parallettes exercises you can do at home. Follow along with me if you're looking for a minimalist workout to build an impressive physique.
